  "slug": "better-leveling",
  "title": "Better Leveling",
  "description": "This mod adds a functional RPG specialization and skill system into Minecraft.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/s1HMvbt/better-leveling.png\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 📖About </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> This mod adds a functional RPG specialization and skill system into Minecraft. </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 26px;\"> Notice! </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> This mod is for <em><strong>Forge</strong></em> only!<br>This mod is still <em><strong>work-in-progress</strong></em>! </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 📘 Features </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> You can choose one of 3 specializations for your first after you reach a certain experience level. <em><strong>(5 by default)</strong></em><br>You can unlock all specializations later down the line by spending your experience levels <em><strong>(30 by default)</strong></em><br>Each specialization gives bonus XP and has 6 skills which you can level up by spending your available experience.<br>A list of all specializations and skills can be found <a href=\"https://github.com/darkorg69/better-leveling/wiki/specializations-&amp;-skills\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">here</span></a>. </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 📷 Media </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\"> After reaching level 5, press <strong>B</strong> and choose your first specialization.<br></span> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/27kyxDP/choose.gif\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\"> Level up your skills!<br></span> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/mbvTvmn/levelupskills.gif\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\"> Unlock other specializations.<br></span> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6wBHbGD/unlockspecs.gif\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 26px;\"> Important! </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> The default key for opening the GUI is <strong>B</strong>.<br>You can always change it from the keybindings menu.<br><br>Please, back up your worlds when you update the game or the mod.<br>In case you don't back up your world data loss or world corruption could occur.<br></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 💡 FAQ's </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> Q: Experiencing bugs/issues while using the mod?<br>A: Please, submit your bug/issue report <a href=\"https://github.com/darkorg69/better-leveling/issues\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">here</span></a>.<br><br>Q: Can I include this mod in my modpack?<br>A: Yes!<br><br>Q: Fabric port?<br>A: <del>I could port this mod to Fabric in the future. Before then, you are free to port it yourself.</del></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A: I'm currently porting this mod to Fabric. Very soon it will be available for all modloaders.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br>Q: My furnace isn't cooking faster?<br>A: Bind the furnace to you, by <strong><em>shift-right-clicking</em></strong> with an empty hand on it. (It works if you are holding a tool too)</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> Credits ❤️ </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> I want to give special credits to <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/beetoguy\">BeetoGuy</a> for the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/level-up\">original mod</a> idea. </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> Make sure to check out my other mods 🤗 </span></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-punching\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xDZbg47/better-punching.png\"> </a></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-materials\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/CtGz93k/better-materials.png\"> </a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-durability\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Mk2gxRm/better-durability.png\"> </a></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/global-block-hardness\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VBYVKRh/global-block-hardness.png\"> </a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>",
